Package org.hibernate.tool.schema.extract.internal.legacy Description

This package follows the legacy behavior of org.hibernate.tool.hbm2ddl.DatabaseMetadata, which is no longer available. org.hibernate.tool.schema.extract.internal is still a work in progress and this package will remain in place until it is finished.
